    <h2>Buff Calculator Steps:</h2>
    <ol>
      <li>Enter your original time (Days, Hours, Minutes, Seconds).</li>
      <li>Enter your total Buff % (including secretary buff %).</li>
      <li>Click "Calculate Buffed Time".</li>
      <li>Click "Apply Manual Speed-Ups & Help Reductions" (Optional).</li>
      <li>Enter your daily speed-up time, how many days to calculate, number of helps, and help-time per help.</li>
      <li>Click "Calculate Final Time".</li>
    </ol>

    <div style="text-align: center;">
