    <h2>Buff Formulas</h2>
    <button onclick="toggleTable()">Show / Hide Formulas</button>
    <div id="formulaTable" style="display: block;">
      <table>
        <tr><th>Step</th><th>Formula</th><th>Description</th></tr>
        <tr><td>1. Buffed Time</td><td>Original Time ÷ (1 + Buff %)</td><td>Time after applying total buff %.</td></tr>
        <tr><td>2. Total Daily Speed-Up</td><td>Daily Speed-Up (sec) × Days</td><td>Speed-up time per day × days.</td></tr>
        <tr><td>3. Total Help Reduction</td><td>Helps × Help Time (sec)</td><td>Time saved from alliance helps.</td></tr>
        <tr><td>4. Final Time</td><td>Buffed Time - Reductions</td><td>Final remaining build time.</td></tr>
      </table>
    </div>

    <hr style="border: 1px solid gold; margin: 20px 0;">

    <h2>RSS Production Calculator Steps:</h2>
    <ol>
      <li>Add entries for each resource (Food, Iron, Gold) with Quantity and Output/hr.</li>
      <li>Enter Buff % for each resource.</li>
      <li>Enter Secretary of Interior sessions/day (optional).</li>
      <li>Click "Calculate All".</li>
    </ol>

