    <h2>Food Production Formulas</h2>
    <button onclick="toggleRSSFormulas()">Show / Hide Formulas</button>
    <div id="rssFormulaTable" style="display: block;">
      <table>
        <tr><th>Step</th><th>Formula</th><th>Description</th></tr>
        <tr><td>1. Base Production</td><td>Σ (Quantity × Output/hr)</td><td>Unbuffed hourly production.</td></tr>
        <tr><td>2. Buffed Production/hr</td><td>Base × (1 + Buff %)</td><td>Buff % applied.</td></tr>
        <tr><td>3. Secretary Bonus</td><td>Buffed/hr × 100%</td><td>Extra 100% during Secretary sessions.</td></tr>
        <tr><td>4. Daily Production</td><td>Buffed/hr × 24 + Bonus/hr × Minutes ÷ 60</td><td>Includes Secretary time.</td></tr>
        <tr><td>5. Weekly & Monthly</td><td>Daily × 7 and Daily × 30</td><td>For long-term planning.</td></tr>
      </table>
